Localization.Name: Vanduul Plushie
Localization.Description: Not all Vanduul crave battle, some crave cuddles. Intricately crafted using a high-grade polyester, this plushie is ready to conquer your heart with its durable plastic armor, felt shoulder pads, and elegant gold detailing.
